The elution time of MIP/Fe3O4@SiO2 was studied and it was found that the elution could be completed within 6 h (Fig. S3). The adsorption capacity of MIP/Fe3O4@SiO2 (Fig. S4
                        ; 
                        Table S1
                        ; 
                        Table S2) as well as the imprinting factors (IF) (Fig. S5) were also investigated.
